{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Heatwave is a <strong>2d fighting game</strong> and <strong>visual novel</strong>, set many years after apocalyptic heatwaves have made most of the Earth uninhabitable. Now, humanity is split between Earth, the Moon, and the Underworld...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take control of 15+ unique fighters in classic game modes, such as Arcade, Survival, Local Vs, Combo Trial, and more! Then, discover their stories through a  visual novel story mode! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">          <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980420/extras/steam_page_art_aprilgroup.png?t=1735931769\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Choose between 3 unique fighting styles, which drastically change how the game plays!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Speed Mode:</strong> A fast, movement and combo based fighting mode, geared towards beginners.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Power Mode:</strong>  Limited movement and cancels, but a stronger parry, higher damage, and special overdrive state to compensate.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Team Mode:</strong> Instead of an assist, pick a second character to fight alongside, and gain access to powerful setups and pressure by switching places with them. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">          <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980420/extras/steam_page_art_raingroup.png?t=1735931769\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735931769","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980420/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735931769","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2980420/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735931769","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati